  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The creature within wriggles whenever the egg is touched, excited by the prospect of hatching.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential for a <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">sweet tempered</span> nature, comforted by gentle touch.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一枚有生命的、可孵化的卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已经准备好孵化！</span><br><br>每次触碰外壳都能感受到里面的生物在不停扭动，迫不及待想要破壳而出。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">温婉</span>的基因潜质，喜欢被轻柔抚摸。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且即將孵化！</span><br><br>一經觸碰，內部的生物就會開始扭動，因夢想孵化而興奮。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下形容的大小及特徵：<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">脾氣好</span>天性，能透過溫和觸摸安撫。"
  },
